      <title>泰晤士水务公司本月不会从股东那里获得 5 亿英镑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/thames-water-won-t-get-500-million-from-shareholders-this-month</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰晤士水务公用事业有限公司表示，扭亏为盈计划所需的第一批 5 亿英镑新股本将不会按预期在 3 月底之前提供。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/thames-water-won-t-get-500-million-from-shareholders-this-month</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:12:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着关系改善，中国取消对澳大利亚葡萄酒的关税</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国取消了对澳大利亚葡萄酒出口的惩罚性关税，标志着对堪培拉长达三年的贸易压力运动的结束，并为这个价值数十亿美元的行业复兴带来了希望。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/china-scraps-tariffs-on-australian-wine-as-relations-improve</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 07:02:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行预计印度债券将有高达 300 亿美元的额外资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-28/stanchart-sees-up-to-30-billion-of-extra-inflows-to-india-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行印度金融市场主管帕鲁尔·米塔尔·辛哈 (Parul Mittal Sinha) 在接受彭博电视台采访时谈到了外国投资者对印度政府债券日益增长的兴趣，以及客户寻求进入该市场的多种方式。 （来源：彭博社）]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2024-03-28/stanchart-sees-up-to-30-billion-of-extra-inflows-to-india-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:56:39 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>渣打银行预计印度债券将新增 300 亿美元资金流入</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/stanchart-sees-30-billion-of-added-inflows-into-indian-bonds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渣打银行 (Standard Chartered Plc) 表示，自 6 月份印度开始被纳入主要全球指数以来，印度债券市场可能会迎来高达 300 亿美元的额外流入。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/stanchart-sees-30-billion-of-added-inflows-into-indian-bonds</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:53:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
