      <title>澳大利亚锂生产商将在线销售以提高透明度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/australian-lithium-producer-to-sell-online-in-transparency-push</link>
      <description><![CDATA[澳大利亚矿商 Mineral Resources Ltd. 将使用数字交易平台出售锂辉石精矿（一种含锂矿物），努力提高市场透明度。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/australian-lithium-producer-to-sell-online-in-transparency-push</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 28 Mar 2024 06:53:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
