      <title>施瓦茨曼看好私人信贷，称违约率为0.3%</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-03-28/schwarzman-bullish-on-private-credit-citing-0-3-default-rate</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Blackstone 首席执行官 Steve Schwarzman 表示，尽管批评者警告该资产类别正在形成泡沫，但私人信贷行业仍将进一步扩张。]]></description>
